## 手順

### 1. projects.yaml 作成

`dashboard/projects.yaml` にプロジェクト一覧を記述:
```yaml
projects:
  - name: dot-claude-dev
    path: /Users/ryryo/dev/dot-claude-dev
  - name: meurai-editer
    path: /Users/ryryo/dev/meurai-editer
  - name: base-ui-design
    path: /Users/ryryo/dev/base-ui-design
  - name: kamui-ryryo
    path: /Users/ryryo/dev/kamui-ryryo
  - name: goosely-editor
    path: /Users/ryryo/dev/goosely-editor
  - name: swipe-lp-builder
    path: /Users/ryryo/dev/swipe-lp-builder
  - name: lead-form
    path: /Users/ryryo/dev/lead-form
